title: League ranked flex.
body: So after 10 promotion matches i didnt get any rank ( division ) ? Its something bugged or  ? :3

replies.body:
It looks like the EUNE server specifically had issues with this that has since been resolved. We addressed this issue on [this post](http://boards.euw.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements-en/xJW1AVbx-resolved-eun-placement-not-occurring-after-completing-10-matches).

Playing your next game should result in you placing properly now. I hope this helped!
Thanks on feedback all good now.
